==In Popular Culture==

* &quot;Demon Copperhead&quot; by Barbara Kingsolver. Inspired by &quot;David Copperfield&quot;, author Charles Dickens, the 2022 novel is set in Lee County. The protagonist, like Copperfield, is born into poverty and becomes an orphan.

